N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 510.6 - Termination

State Regulations
(a) The application
deadline for this program is 60 days from the date this Part is filed with the
office of the Secretary of State and shall continue through any subsequent
period of extension made by SEMO in its discretion. Information regarding any
such extension shall be made available by SEMO. Unless an extension occurs, all
applications must be postmarked by July 15, 1999 to be eligible for
consideration for the program. (b) Unless extended in accordance with subdivision (a) of this section, applications received which are not postmarked by July 15, 1999 will not be
considered for the program or acknowledged. Notes
